data.description: Welcome home to this spacious townhouse in a convenient Owings Mills, Maryland location. This home boasts 3 bedrooms, including a den that could serve as a potential 4th bedroom on the lower level. With 2 full bathrooms and 2 half bathrooms, there's a bathroom on every level, including a full bathroom in the owner's suite. Don't judge a book by its cover; this house offers ample space for both indoor and outdoor entertaining. Plus, you'll enjoy easy access to major roadways, public transportation, shopping, and dining options.
